{"word":"Shittim","slug":"shittim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shittim</b> <a href=\"#/H7851\">H7851</a> <br/> 1. Called Abel-Shittim:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=49'>Num 33:49</a> <br/> - A camping place of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=25&verse=1'>Num 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=49'>Num 33:49</a> <br/> - Joshua sends spies from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=2&verse=1'>Jos 2:1</a> <br/> - Valley of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=18'>Joe 3:18</a> <br/> - Balaam prophesies in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=5'>Mic 6:5</a> <br/> 2. Called Shittah, a tree, the wood of which is fragrant:<br/> - Planted and cultivated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=41&verse=19'>Isa 41:19</a> <br/> - The ark of the covenant made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=10'>Exo 25:10</a> <br/> - Staves of the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=13'>Exo 25:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=6'>Exo 38:6</a> <br/> - Boards in the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=37'>Exo 26:37</a> <br/> - The altar of burnt offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=1'>Exo 38:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=6'>Exo 38:6</a> "}]}